# Post-prompt build verification

After completing every user prompt in this project (including question-only prompts), run:

```bash
npm run build
```

from the project root (`d:\Projects\toys`).

- Run build even when no files were changed
- If build fails, fix errors before ending the turn
- Do not skip build because the task was small or read-only
- Dev server (`npm run dev`) may run in parallel; build uses `.next` separately
